            <description>A plump figure of spotted skin stretched over an impossibly rotund humanoid frame. The origins of Mr Blobbys's name is unknown.\n\nOutlander folklore describes an invisible spectre that captures the minds of sinners, placing them in a living hell. In the story, the victims can only be returned to life by hunting the creature as it sleeps and killing it.\n\nA hidden Mr Blobby can be revealed with disruptor flares, explosives, EMP, firefoam, or fire.</description>
